flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Receive User Question]
    B --> C[Initialize Research Agent]
    subgraph InnerAgent["Inner Agent Loop"]
    C --> D{Search or Answer?}
    D -->|Search| E[Execute Web Search]
    E --> F[Collect Search Results]
    F --> G[Reason over Results]
    G --> D
    D -->|Answer| H[Generate Candidate Answer]
    end
    H --> I[Submit to Supervisor]
    subgraph Supervisor["Supervisor Validation"]
    I --> J{Answer Valid?}
    J -->|Valid| K[Accept Answer]
    J -->|"Nonsensical or<br/>Fabricated"| L[Reject Answer]
    end
    K --> M([Return Verified Answer])
    L --> N[Force Retry]
    N --> C